					    <div class="CalendarListItemDetails">
						    <h3><a class="linklist" href="/en/dep/lmd/the-ministry-of-agriculture-and-food/minister-of-agriculture-and-food-lars-pe/kalender/2010-3/muntlige-sporretimen-i-stortinget.html?id=620291">Muntlig spørretimen i Stortinget</a></h3>
						    <p>Landbruks- og matminister Lars Peder Brekk vil delta i den muntlige spørretimen i Stortinget.</p>
					    </div>
				    </div>    						
			    				
				    <div class="CalendarListItem">
					    <div id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_ctl00_calendarList_ctl03_CalendarListItemDate" class="CalendarListItemDate">
					        12:00
					    </div>
					    <div class="CalendarListItemDetails">
						    <h3><a class="linklist" href="/en/dep/fad/about-the-ministry/minister-of-reform-and-church-affairs-ri/utdrag-fra-statsrad-rigmor-aasruds-kalen/2010/Oktober/nettmote-i-vart-land.html?id=619554">Nettmøte i Vårt Land</a></h3>
						    <p>Fornyings-, administrasjons- og kirkeminister Rigmor Aasrud deltar i nettmøte i Vårt Land.</p>
					    </div>
				    </div>    						
			    				
				    <div class="CalendarListItem">
					    <div id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_ctl00_calendarList_ctl04_CalendarListItemDate" class="CalendarListItemDate">
					        12:00
					    </div>
					    <div class="CalendarListItemDetails">
						    <h3><a class="linklist" href="/en/dep/kd/About-the-Ministry/minister-of-research-and-higher-educatio/kalender/2010/Kick-off-konferanse---EUs-8-rammeprogram-for-forskning.html?id=616101">”Kick-off”-konferanse - EUs 8. rammeprogram for forskning</a></h3>
