					    </div>
					    <div class="CalendarListItemDetails">
						    <h3><a class="linklist" href="/en/dep/fad/about-the-ministry/minister-of-reform-and-church-affairs-ri/utdrag-fra-statsrad-rigmor-aasruds-kalen/2010/Oktober/Hovedavtalen-75-ar.html?id=619558">Hovedavtalen 75 år</a></h3>
