					    </div>
					    <div class="CalendarListItemDetails">
						    <h3><a class="linklist" href="/en/dep/aid/about-the-ministry/minister-of-labour-hanne-bjurstrom/kalender/arbeidsministeren-deltar-under-markering.html?id=614702">Hovedavtalen 75 år</a></h3>
